  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I-- I was trying different sorts of business, you see, because he said that he doesn't want me in his firm, but he will finance me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the conditions he gave me-- I said, look, I better go home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you see, the question is that I had a bit of a fight.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You see, they returned to me the status that means, how to have some enough money-- what I left with Australia-- because you see, when I sold the belt business and collected all the thing, I had something like 15,000 pounds, which was money in 1957.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they settled.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in the meantime, [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Robin ?] had an ulcer on his stomach and it was to be operated, and I wanted to be with him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I sent my wife and Lola and Ann back to Melbourne, and they bunked with friends.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And on the way back, you see, after Romak's operation-- everything was all right-- I went to America to look for business.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you see, I had sort of connections, and you see, a fellow who did business with my brother.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went to the Atlantic City for the weekend, and over there was a meeting exhibition.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I lacked some articles, you see-- elastic.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I knew that at that time, there was import restrictions, and if I sort of can get a couple of machines like that, I can do a living in this.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you see, we were sitting in his place and looking at the Yellow Pages.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we went, instead of buying a new machine, I had to go and buy a secondhand machine from a manufacturer, in the meantime, who would teach me how to do it.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
